Package games

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EGAUtils
    Contains several global static utilities, including random number generation, string builders, formatters, etc.
    Game
    This is a (slightly) modified version of the gamut Game class.
    GameGenerator
    Uses Gamut.jar to generate games.
    GameObserver
    Abstract class for observing a game matrix.
    GamutParser
    Class for reading a game from a file in the Gamut "SimpleOutput" format
    MatrixGame
    Class implements the straightforward normal form game.
    MixedStrategy
    A class the encapsulates the notion of a mixed strategy: the probability of playing each action, summing to 1
    OutcomeDistribution
    Represents a distribution over outcomes in a game
    OutcomeIterator
    An Iterator for looping through the outcomes in the game
    Payoffs
    Holds the payoffs for a profile
